WEBVTT

00:00.592 --> 00:01.922
My name is Elena Gilbert.

00:01.924 --> 00:04.458
I'm a new vampire, and there
have been complications.

00:04.460 --> 00:06.221
I know that I'm
sired to you, Damon.

00:06.222 --> 00:07.622
You know what would
make me happy?

00:07.624 --> 00:09.707
That what you
actually felt for me was real.

00:09.709 --> 00:11.009
Elena, voice-over:
But there's hope now.

00:11.011 --> 00:12.844
Woman: Jeremy's tattoo
leads to a cure.

00:12.846 --> 00:14.679
Elena, voice-over:
If you kill Klaus's brother Kol,

00:14.681 --> 00:17.215
their entire sire line
will die with them.

00:17.217 --> 00:20.768
I was gonna make him
suffer on my terms!

00:22.638 --> 00:25.473
Man: Unlikely alliances
have formed.

00:25.475 --> 00:27.475
Finding the cure could
come at a price.

00:27.477 --> 00:29.360
Silas is the world's
first immortal being

00:29.362 --> 00:31.429
who just happens
to be imprisoned with the cure.

00:31.431 --> 00:32.980
I want to free him.

00:32.982 --> 00:35.450
Man: We'll be fine when
we have everything we need.

00:35.452 --> 00:36.784
Here we go.

